[06:33.05]	But win the noble Brutus to our party--
[06:35.66]CASSIUS	Be you content: good Cinna, take this paper,
[06:38.51]	And look you lay it in the praetor's chair,
[06:41.41]	Where Brutus may but find it; and throw this
[06:44.38]	In at his window; set this up with wax
[06:46.99]	Upon old Brutus' statue: all this done,
